{"tid":971411,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"點解rolex d錶文又得 武又得 仲要好睇","createTime":"2019-01-06T15:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T14:39:36.000Z","uid":107362,"like":8,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5876fb0534260f35b2a204bc45cd6fda2aac8e6e","tid":971411,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYFQ7gx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYFQ7gx.png&h=e4da4b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nk4Zf9S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNk4Zf9S.png&h=43c7050a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好難有一隻款兩邊都合適唔突兀<br />\n一係太斯文 一係太sporty 兩邊都夾又無rolex個種格調<br />\n就算跑步戴rolex都好睇<br />\n依家見d友西裝襯apple watch始終都係格格不入<br />\n<br />\n當然世界好大 你可能見過日本唔知邊個工匠師整左隻超越到rolex既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如有不妨po黎睇睇<br />\n<br />\n最後一點就係 係你戴隻錶 唔係錶戴你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4382b0414839ccf97721f3e7da7ec189293770c","tid":971411,"uid":79793,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:12:26.000Z","msg":"Rolex賣三千既話你就唔會咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7ab626d2431760b497d2b019f96ee2544bcdaa","tid":971411,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4382b0414839ccf97721f3e7da7ec189293770c","tid":971411,"uid":79793,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:12:26.000Z","msg":"Rolex賣三千既話你就唔會咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:15:42.000Z","msg":"不過有d抄黑水鬼既錶都可以做到呢個效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係想知點解呢隻款咁萬能"},{"pid":"f90ec10d106374bf35798cd28eb227f8de51bd01","tid":971411,"uid":28307,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b4382b0414839ccf97721f3e7da7ec189293770c","tid":971411,"uid":79793,"like":36,"dislike":